    Create a new module in Magento.
    Create a new database table product_pincode using db_schema.xml file.
    Create a new UI component to display the form for adding pin codes to products using ui_component/product_pincode_form.xml file.
    Create a new Controller to save pin codes for the products.
    Add the pin code form to the Product edit page using a plugin for Magento\Catalog\Block\Adminhtml\Product\Edit\Tabs.
    Create a new block to display product availability based on pin code using Block/ProductAvailability.php file.
    Create a new template to display product availability based on pin code using view/frontend/templates/product/view/availability.phtml file.
    Add the "Check Availability" button to the product view page using a plugin for Magento\Catalog\Block\Product\View.
    Implement the logic to check product availability based on pin code in Block/ProductAvailability.php file.
    Add the necessary JavaScript code to handle the button click event and to display the product availability message in the view/frontend/templates/product/view/availability.phtml file.
